# uglify-to-browserify

A transform to make UglifyJS work in browserify.

[![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/ForbesLindesay/uglify-to-browserify.png?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/ForbesLindesay/uglify-to-browserify) [![Dependency Status](https://gemnasium.com/ForbesLindesay/uglify-to-browserify.png)](https://gemnasium.com/ForbesLindesay/uglify-to-browserify) [![NPM version](https://badge.fury.io/js/uglify-to-browserify.png)](http://badge.fury.io/js/uglify-to-browserify)

## Installation

npm install uglify-to-browserify
